snippet.title: WHAT THE CAR? Steam Date Announcement - PLAY THE DEMO!
snippet.description:
🚗Play the demo and wishlist now!🚗  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2727650/WHAT_THE_CAR/  

WHAT THE CAR? is an absurd racing adventure about a car with legs!
Race through hundreds of unique levels by jumping, flying with jetpacks, climbing buildings, delivering packages, and pretty much everything you would NOT expect a car to do.

From the creators of WHAT THE GOLF? and WHAT THE BAT? comes the new DICE Award winner WHAT THE CAR? which is officially launching on Steam on September 5th 2024.
